# BubbleMenu Components Rule

The [index.vue](mdc:src/components/BubbleMenu/index.vue), [ColorSelector.vue](mdc:src/components/BubbleMenu/ColorSelector.vue), [LinkSelector.vue](mdc:src/components/BubbleMenu/LinkSelector.vue), and [NodeSelector.vue](mdc:src/components/BubbleMenu/NodeSelector.vue) components follow shadcn-vue conventions:

- Each is a single file component (SFC) in the `src/components/BubbleMenu` directory.
- Used for contextual editing menus and selectors.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.

For contextual menu best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Dropdown Menu documentation](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/dropdown-menu).



